{"type": "article", "id": 30612, "title": "全球最大奢侈电商上半年利好，以及，H&M 新品宣称“简单的奢华” | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-05T02:24:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 2273, "name": "乐天"}, {"id": 9086, "name": "Starbucks"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160805095419RnQaxJFAZVTtUGPj.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/adidas-confirms-strong-q2-results-as-u-s-gains-steam-10501470/\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 第二季度销售大涨</a> | 该季度集团总营收为 44 亿欧元，销售额增长了 25.6%，在西欧的收入增长了 29.2%，中国作为增长最快的地区，实现了 30.1% 的增长。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/dolce-gabbana-plans-job-cuts-sources-say-10501495/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dolce &amp; Gabbana 要裁员</a> | 这个意大利的时装公司计划裁掉米兰周边 Legnano 工厂的部分员工。有分析师认为，前 Gucci 的 CEO 是这次 D&amp;G 裁员事件背后的主谋，而这次的裁员则是一个更广泛的公司重组计划的开端。</p><p class=\"\">全球最大<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/ynap-profits-sales-grow-first-half-10501857/\" rel=\"nofollow\">奢侈品电商 Yoox Net-a-porter &nbsp;上半年收入可观</a> | 2016 年上半年，YNAP 的净利润上涨了 15.2% ，为 3700 万欧元。包括 Net-a-porter, Mr Porter, Porter, Thecorner 和 Shoescribe 在内的销售当季设计师品牌的电商网站对集团业绩提升影响较大。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/under-armour-bill-besselman-joins-textile-start-up-thread-10501801/\" rel=\"nofollow\">前 Under Armour CEO Bill Besselman 加入了初创公司 Thread</a> | 可持续性纺织材料研发公司 Thread，聘请了前 Under Armour CEO Bill Besselman，他将指导品牌的整体发展，为其建立关键的销售渠道。<br></p><h3><span>一些值得一看的：</span></h3><p>全球奢侈品电商 NET-A-PORTER 选了一批酷女孩，在纽约市中心，拍摄了一组<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/net-a-porter-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">秋冬时尚大片。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235321wxOEldSuN6Kj8kzb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235348WZ5fovU46wsiDmd8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235409P4j0hOQx9DBqyLpC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">G-Dragon 和 Taeyang 为韩国时尚品牌 JUUN.J 代言，拍摄了一组<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/g-dragon-taeyang-juun-j-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\">暗黑时尚大片。</a><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160805083607CUop5ak0nM3GyQgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160805083615VufqKIlcvUyREpZj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160805083624wnfaHKOSQ79ZqPid.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>意大利皮革品牌 Furla 发布了<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/furla-2016-fall-winter-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">秋冬季新款广告片</a>，俏皮又时尚。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235443p9X5eHgGRfcjoFyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235456J6xPnaNktVDG2L47.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608042355047FR23UyoicLJHxQs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Starbucks 推出日本 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/starbucks-ginza-japan-20-years\" rel=\"nofollow\">20 周年限定系列</a>，只限六家店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235612kgcWa9zDJUIEYPnl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235622HBcgZxrREWL79wa2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\"><br></p><p>H&amp;M 发布了一组新的时尚大片，主打“<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/lounge-ready-outfits-hm-shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Easy Luxe”风格</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235726Fs3BiVHwko87pCXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235719YcExnv6IqXtKNpyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804235709QSKj4eCzk3qGIw8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}